Info about project 
--------------------------------------------------------------------

Twitter lib: tweepy
Database: sqlite

--------------------------------------------------------------------
   
python manage.py syncdb   - to create database with tables

--------------------------------------------------------------------

Put your configuration file (twitter.cnf) into the root directory. 

--------------------------------------------------------------------

python manage.py runserver
Go to 'http://127.0.0.1:8000/filldb/it' (to fill IT category in your database).

!!!  it - default category  !!!

'http://127.0.0.1:8000' - home page
'http://127.0.0.1:8000/categories' - home page
'http://127.0.0.1:8000/{category}'  - category's page
/updatedb/{category}   - update category
/filldb/{category}  - fill category

'http://127.0.0.1:8000/updatedb/it' (to update IT category in your database)

!!!  /updatedb/{category}  /filldb/{category}  - temporary pages for testing  !!!
--------------------------------------------------------------------

